images.description: Chunky, bold black lines outline four semi-abstract figures that stand at the edge of a pond, indicated by a large black half-oval extending in from the left. A grassy shore and dense vegetation are indicated by bright green shapes that mass along the bottom, curve around the right side, and then recede in the distance beyond the pond along the top. Two figures at right stand in the foreground on the shore, holding thin reeds, while the other two do likewise, just beyond them in shallow water at center-left. While they lack distinct facial features, the figures, simplified pale orange shapes, show animated gestures.
images.alttext: Four nude figures stand on the shore of a pond, amid dense foliage
